School of Computer Science and Engineering (SCOPE)
Cordially invites you all for 8th Module Guest Lecture on
"Role of Cryptocurrencies in Digital Money Exchange"
Mr. Arjun Vijay
Expertise : Cryptocurrency
by
Mr. Arjun Vijay
Co-Founder and Chief Operating Officer
Giottus Cryptocurrency Exchange, Chennai
Arjun Vijay is the Co-Founder and Chief Operating Officer (COO) of Giottus Cryptocurrency
Exchange, one of India's leading digital assets trading platforms. In his current role, he is
responsible for spearheading the day-to-day operations Of Giottus as well as in fortifring its
product suite and partnerships. His passion and interest in cryptocurrency helped him ideate and
create a world-class trading platform with sophisticated tools in an easy-to-use app. He has been
instrumental in helping Giottus acquire plus customers across India. Arjun is focused
on new product development with strong customer-centricity. Arjun, an alumnus of 11M
Calcutta, has initiated multiple scalable consumer programs successfully throughout his career.
He believes in the value of innovation and considers this as a journey towards creating the go-to
platform for investment in virtual assets. He experiences across diverse domains — retail,
telecom, renewable energy and blockchain — help him on this path and keep him grounded to
consumer realities.
Date: 28th September, 2022 (Wednesday)
Time: 02.00 PM to 03.30 PM
Venue: SJT-507
All are invited
Faculty Coordinators: Dr. GOPICHAND G
